<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grant Application Update - MaalEdu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #dc2626);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .reason-box {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 2px solid #fca5a5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .reason-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #dc2626;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ea580c;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .support-box {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Grant Application Update</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Grant Application Status</h2>
            <p>Hi <%= userName %>,</p>

            <p>Thank you for your interest in our grant program for <strong>
                    <%= courseTitle %>
                </strong>. We appreciate the time and effort you put into your application.</p>

            <p>Unfortunately, we are unable to approve your grant application at this time.</p>

            <% if (typeof reason !=='undefined' && reason) { %>
                <div class="reason-box">
                    <p class="reason-text"><strong>Reason:</strong>
                        <%= reason %>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                    <div class="support-box">
                        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #ea580c;">Don't Give Up!</h3>
                        <p>We encourage you to:</p>
                        <ul style="text-align: left; display: inline-block;">
                            <li>Apply again in the future when more slots become available</li>
                            <li>Explore our regular enrollment options with payment plans</li>
                            <li>Check for upcoming scholarship opportunities</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <a href="https://maaledu.com/courses" class="btn">Explore Our Courses â†’</a>
                    </div>

                    <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
                        <strong>Questions?</strong> Feel free to reach out to our support team for guidance on
                        alternative learning options.
                    </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>We appreciate your interest in blockchain education!<br>The MaalEdu Team</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <a href="https://maaledu.com" style="color: #ea580c;">maaledu.com</a> |
                <a href="mailto:support@maaledu.com" style="color: #ea580c;">support@maaledu.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>